State COVID-19 Cases

library(tidyverse)

library(coronavirusbrazil)
data("spatial_br_states")

head(spatial_br_states)
#> # A tibble: 6 x 13
#>   id    name  uf    codigo regiao geometry date       cases deaths delta_cases
#>   
#> 1 AC    Acre  AC        12 Norte       2020-04-04    46      0           0
#> 2 AL    Alag~ AL        27 Norde~      2020-04-04    23      2           1
#> 3 AM    Amaz~ AM        13 Norte       2020-04-04   311     12          51
#> 4 AP    Amapá AP        16 Norte       2020-04-04    28      1           9
#> 5 BA    Bahia BA        29 Norde~      2020-04-04   332      7          50
#> 6 CE    Ceará CE        23 Norde~      2020-04-04   730     22         103
#> # ... with 3 more variables: delta_deaths , log_cases ,
#> #   log_deaths 
mapview::mapview(spatial_br_states, 
                 map = leaflet::leaflet() %>% leaflet::addTiles(),
                 zcol="cases", cex="log_cases")
